  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was still holding that chocolate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were-- in that place was a pump where people used to go for water-- in the middle, a big pump there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he grabbed the foot with that child, and he knocked it against the whole body.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was swinging around like you see that sport which you take the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the gavel?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The things [INAUDIBLE] this, you know, which has a thing like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was twisting it around a number of times, and he hit that little child against that pump, and-- and smashed his head to pieces.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You have a hard time to adjust your mind to switch so quickly from a human being to a vicious animal.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually an animal wouldn't do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was hysterically laughing what was two other things there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he took the thing, and he throwed it away, the child there and then he kicked it over there and was want to make sure.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the-- and I saw the mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was grabbing her hair, tearing-- [SOBBING] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tearing her hair-- hair out, from this, like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took out the gun, and he shot her right in the face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, her face split to pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, in a most calm way, he took off his gloves, and he throwed it on that child, [INAUDIBLE] like, well, those gloves were contaminated.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he laughed, and the other one took pictures of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, how can you tell something like this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I must say, there is not a pen, there is not a human mind can actually describe that horrifying picture, which have took place maybe in five minutes' time.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
